title: Cartoons:  Super Friends Shorts 1980-1983
description:
I bought a DVD off of eBay.  I thought that it was going to the be the official factory release of The Super Friends, it turned out to be a bootleg copy of TV Rips.  Much to my surprise these SuperFriends shorts were on one of the DVD&#039;s..  These "shorts" are all under 7 minutes long and some of them have different Super Heroes along side the regular bunch of Super Friends.  Some of the other heroes are:
The Atom
The Wonder Twins
Apache Chief
Green Lantern
Hawkman and Hawkwoman
The Flash
and more......
